<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    /* Add CSS styles here */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .message {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="header">Welcome to Our Healthcare Community</h2>
    <p>Dear {{patientName}},</p>
    <div class="message">
      <p>We want to express our gratitude for creating an account as a patient in our healthcare community. Your patient registration has been confirmed. Here are your registration details:</p>
      <p><strong>Email: {{patientEmail}}</strong></p>
      <p>You can use the provided email and password to log in to your patient account and access our healthcare services. We recommend changing your password for security reasons after your initial login.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at {{supportEmail}}.</p>
    </div>
    <p>Thank you for choosing our healthcare service for your medical needs.</p>
    <p>Sincerely,<br>The Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
